articles.title: Ukraine will gemeinsame Waffenproduktion mit Polen
articles.image_title: WARSAW, POLAND - APRIL 05: Ukraine's President Volodymyr Zelenskyy addresses the attendees inside the courtyard of the Royal Castle, on April 05, 2023, in Warsaw, Poland. President Zelensky's one-day trip to Poland involved talks with top officials and addressing both the Polish and Ukrainian communities. The discussions covered key issues such as security, economic cooperation, historical matters, agriculture, and transport of Ukrainian grain through Poland, aimed at strengthening bilateral ties. Stringer / Anadolu Agency
